{"tid":2505904,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"半億噴泉嘔泡即封 專家稱梘液無阻運作 反憂霧化嬉水勁播病毒","createTime":"2021-04-27T03:26:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T03:32:45.000Z","uid":12458,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5c427e72e7fe2ef3f3c24808edc583b87fd01083","tid":2505904,"uid":12458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:26:16.000Z","msg":"節錄-<br />\n耗資半億公帑的觀塘音樂噴泉，啟用不足2天已地板不平，須圍封維修。「100毛」藝人東方昇日前到場以梘液「沐浴」拍攝節目。康文署繼不點名批評對方欠公德後，昨午（26日）又聲稱池水因梘液引致大量泡沫，要關閉消毒。惟前工程師盧覺強指出，梘液泡沫根本無阻機件運件。化學博士K. Kwong亦稱，肥皂或液態清潔劑根本不堵喉管，反而擔心嬉水區霧化池水，如同散播病毒的超級裝置，令很多嬉水的人易交叉感染。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210427/L7LRLUZFNRHOBJ236VBCAMZQEE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210427%2FL7LRLUZFNRHOBJ236VBCAMZQEE%2F&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B61KEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=4f00da51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210427%2FL7LRLUZFNRHOBJ236VBCAMZQEE%2F&h=9f51bd04\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210427/L7LRLUZFNRHOBJ236VBCAMZQEE/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>原來咁岩搵到個藉口封池驚大爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d576719a05dadce5a8792d5f3fffd1a90095282f","tid":2505904,"uid":253626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:27:04.000Z","msg":"鮑姐有冇大爆發？"},{"pid":"356d553a6cf4c3a14bd9c8df583a277bc46f0885","tid":2505904,"uid":126352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:27:19.000Z","msg":"梘液鮑姐倒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5ea10ca4fec9c678854b5f78b0ff2059a2fae4","tid":2505904,"uid":161274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:27:44.000Z","msg":"鮑姐有冇去玩泡泡"},{"pid":"9b887d6906b40585f6cf2d9bfa7aecbaff150f8e","tid":2505904,"uid":18636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cit